{"tid":1294451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警方旺角清場驅散示威者 多人被按在地上遭制伏","createTime":"2019-07-07T19:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T19:05:48.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f99c01774d940e853d52d42ac7f7c2d767aae29d","tid":1294451,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:03:09.000Z","msg":"一批反修訂《逃犯條例》的示威者晚上在旺角聚集，警方晚上11時前採取驅散行動，用警棍拍向示威者舉起的雨傘，並拘捕多名示威者，將他們按在地上，扣上手銬。部分示威者的前額及口罩沾滿血跡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pt4XhZB_bXmcbx5agZts8w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-07/9dc4e550-a0cc-11e9-afd1-a3c261d0559f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fpt4XhZB_bXmcbx5agZts8w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-07%2F9dc4e550-a0cc-11e9-afd1-a3c261d0559f&h=d1ed6d51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批警員在亞皆老街與彌敦道交界、豉油街以及山東街一帶布防，最前排的警員戴上頭盔，配備盾牌、胡椒噴霧或催淚水劑。多部警車在場戒備，阻止示威者向前推進。示威者撐起雨傘阻擋，亦有人跑離現場。<br />\n<br />\n警方在行動前，多次向示威者發出警告，說他們參與非法集結，要立即離開，否則使用武力驅散。"},{"pid":"12a8986320e37c05b65e9d45a4830c5e9c6adef4","tid":1294451,"uid":117893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.lapresse.ca/international/asie-et-oceanie/201907/07/01-5232988-hong-kong-charge-policiere-a-lissue-dune-nouvelle-manif-monstre.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lapresse.ca%2Finternational%2Fasie-et-oceanie%2F201907%2F07%2F01-5232988-hong-kong-charge-policiere-a-lissue-dune-nouvelle-manif-monstre.php&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=aee56f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lapresse.ca/international/asie-et-oceanie/201907/07/01-5232988-hong-kong-charge-policiere-a-lissue-dune-nouvelle-manif-monstre.php</a>"}]}